  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 05/09/2022 at 11:30pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.18.5-Improvements\">Improvements</h3><ul><li><p>A new in-app help tool has been turned on for our users.</p></li><li><p>Updated security for Square, specifically to delete and refresh tokens when the user revokes access.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.5-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Attempting to save or close a Return Repair no longer returns an Error 500.</p></li><li><p>Attempting to reconcile or cancel Inventory Counts no longer returns false errors.</p></li><li><p>Resolved an issue with tips during the refund process.</p></li><li><p>The Refurbish Ticket Print Label button now works again as intended.</p></li><li><p>Fixed a problem that prevented the customer portal Qsite Logo from being uploaded unless dragged and dropped in.</p></li></ul>",
